                        <interp inst="t18390708-2056-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. Aged 32.—<rs id="t18390708-2056-punishment-46" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18390708-2056-punishment-46" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-2056-18390708 t18390708-2056-punishment-46"></join>Transnorted for Seven Years</rs>.</p>
